== Handling dead links ==
It's possible that a URL no longer references hosted content, or ends up hosting different content than intended. In this case, the {{tlx|Official website}} should be replaced with an invocation of {{tlx|webarchive}} with a <code>title=</code> parameter of "Official website". For example: <code><nowiki>{{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051222144340/http://en.wikipedia.org/ |date=2005-12-22 |title=Official website}}</nowiki></code>. Such an invocation appears as:

:{{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20051222144340/http://en.wikipedia.org/ |date=2005-12-22 |title=Official website}}

